This is a forked version of https://github.com/jeromegn/Backbone.localStorage/blob/master/backbone.localStorage.js
Support for CRUD in chrome local storage [https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/storage.html]
Normal Backbone.sycn is avaialble as ajaxSync
Chrome local storage is asynchronous[different from default localStorage] and can store objects directly.
Using backbone for packaged chrome apps to work offline needed support for sync.As default localStorage is forbidden in manifest version 2, forked the localStorage adapter of jeromegn.

